                                                        <a href="https://www.marcoimperiale.com" class="icon website margin-left-5" target="_blank">Website</a>
                                                <div class="bio"><p class="small">Marco is a lawyer and the innovation officer at a leading Italian law firm, LCA. As innovation officer, he explores new and global trends in law, with a view to leverage on new technologies to deliver better legal services to clients. As lawyer, he advises national and international clients, primarily regarding copyright and entertainment law. He has a wide experience working with startups, both as mentor, lawyer and negotiation advocate. Marco collaborates with Harward Law School as Teaching Fellow for the CopyrightX course. He has also given seminars and spoke at numerous panel discussions on copyright/entertainment law, and negotiation/mediation.</p></div>
                                                </div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3" id="margaret-hagan">
                                                <div class="image"><img src="images/speakers/margaret-hagan.png"></div>
                                                <p class="margin-bottom-10">Margaret Hagan<br><span class="small">Director, Stanford Legal Design Lab</span></p>
                                                <div class="margin-bottom-30">
                                                        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/margaret-hagan-a7b18941" class="icon linkedin margin-right-5" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
